definitions.definition: A male given name from Scottish Gaelic, variant of Ewan .
A village in Kemble and Ewen parish, Cotswold district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref SU0097 ) .
An unincorporated community and census-designated place in McMillan Township, Ontonagon County , Michigan , United States .
